{"tid":871884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"揚言做星媽　鄭欣宜帶特別嘉賓現身","createTime":"2018-10-22T09:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T11:06:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28b0841243818255d7ab28407e0f2cc2bc488be3","tid":871884,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"歌手鄭欣宜（Joyce）以大使身份出席多元性別活動，第三年出席的她特別為活動製作Medley及排舞，希望炒熱現場氣氛，又笑言帶了特別嘉賓出席，就是其愛犬，幸好牠不怕人多：「佢OK，好易抱走佢。（同佢一齊做嘢？）要佢做搖錢樹？冇問題，我做星媽！之前帶佢沖涼同剪毛，同影咗輯萬聖節相，好得意！」 <br />\n<br />\n講到「一代大俠」岳華逝世，Joyce表示從網上得知消息時，即向身在加拿大的家人求證，證實後覺得很突然和可惜，大讚對方對自己及家人都很好：「佢好仁慈同溫柔，希望佢一路好走。我最後一次見佢係2月，佢知我媽咪死忌，同我一齊食點心，當時佢精神同面色都好好，係瘦咗啲。」她希望有機會出席喪禮，但暫時不想打擾岳華遺孀，只是傳訊息問候岳華女兒，獲對方回覆「多謝」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181021/photo/bkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_01b.jpg?20181022050631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181021%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20181022050631&h=03879258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181021/photo/bkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_02b.jpg?20181022050631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181021%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20181022050631&h=5b993b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181021/photo/bkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_03b.jpg?20181022050631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181021%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181021203003136-1021_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20181022050631&h=dabc5e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81316c295483939978ab93bf6c5633506c1f16e1","tid":871884,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"肥婆又消費死人"},{"pid":"c3504bb47511d1db95c6882d2290149281b31196","tid":871884,"uid":68